description: MediXall Group, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, develops and operates a healthcare marketplace platform to help consumers learn, decide, and pay for healthcare in ways that complement relationships with trusted doctors in the United States. The company offers Health Karma platform that provides medical and wellness services to individuals, employer groups, and third-party administrators. MediXall Group, Inc. was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Fort Lauderdale, Florida.
